body: A few months ago Nintendo ~~was secretly bought by disney~~ started going nuts and blocked soundtracks that have been on youtube for years, of all things. Well, smg4 and onyxking use a lot of nintendo music in every one of their videos, so nintendo is probably going to order youtube to delete their whole channels. This also applies to any lets players or speedrunners, as they have nintendo music in their videos. What's next, banning Mario from YouTube entirely?
